ongly depends on the cognitive task\nconsidered. These results emphasize the importance of understanding the\nfundamental logic processes that contribute to information flow in cognitive\nprocessing, and quantifying their relevance in any given nervous system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jan 2019 19:19:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Dec 2019 04:20:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
