y of the smaller of the two co-orbitals can be significantly\nincreased during the inward migration of the co-orbital pair, which can have a\nsignificant impact on the detectability by transit of such configurations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jan 2019 23:13:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Nov 2019 11:10:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-20"}
