 iterative\nLMMSE detection outperforms the state-of-art methods and is within 0.8dB from\nthe associated capacity limit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jan 2019 05:34:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-27"}
