 periodic cycles are known as the 11-year Schwabe and 22-year Hale solar\ncycles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jan 2019 17:52:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Feb 2019 20:18:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-11"}
